Yasmin Said (/ˈsaɪd/) bụ onye Kenya na-eme ihe nkiri nke natara ihe nrite maka Best Lead Actress in TV Drama na Kalasha Awards n'afọ 2020. A mụrụ Said na 7 Ọktoba 2000 ma zụlite ya na Nairobi
Ruo afọ 2021, ọ bụ onye nnọchi anya Indomie.
Said ritere ihe nrite maka Best Lead Actress na TV Drama na Kalasha Awards n'afọ 2020 maka usoro Maria na Citizen Tv.
